task.summary: Initial commit; Basic API set up for creating/getting game. Game model and service set up with necessary actions. Added InMemoryRepository for storing games. Tests added for model and repository. Service tests still need to be created.
Added further unit tests. Cleaned up controllers to return dto objects instead of backend objects.
Refactored game implementation to be more object oriented using objects for pieces of game instead of just int arrays. Updated and added new tests.
